        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-6">
            If you don‚Äôt receive an email, check your spam folder or
            <a href="{{ path('app_forgot_password_request') }}" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">try again</a>.
